name: Stickman Skyblock: Multicraft
description:
Go in survival with new multicraft stickman skyblock!

Stickman is addictive game, go in realistic pixel art game with perfect graphics.

** STICKMAN CRAFT FEATURES **
• Too much items for crafting
• Amazing graphics
• Amazing sounds
• Creating so many machines
• Realistic animation with crafting

Start crafting and survival in the land.
In Stickman Skyblock you can collect and craft with so many items.
So Stick Multicraft game is free, and in new updates, it will come with new levels and new amazing characters that comes with new items.

Then, do not wait, download game for free and tell us what do you think, how we can improve game in new skyblock land.

If you have any questions please contact us on mail.
Enjoy the game!
